Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present this first class offering for sale or lease.

1 Altona Street, Bibra Lake is a well located, functional industrial facility with good quality two level offices and modern high truss warehousing presenting in an overall good quality.

Stand alone industrial building located on the corner of Port Kembla Drive and Altona Street.

Exceptional access and rear yard with secure perimeter fencing.

For further details and an inspection please contact the listing agent.

These units offer the perfect opportunity to lease a large, recently developed office / warehouse.  Comprising two level air conditioned offices, large roller door access, full concrete panel and driveways, provision for 10T gantry crane, 9 metre truss height, ample parking and many more features.

The Bibra Lake Industrial area has been transformed over the last 15 years by two new subdivisions, with Cockburn Commercial Park developed by Landcorp and Phoenix Business Park development by Primewest.  Both estates are now completed with limited vacant sites that are yet to be developed.  These new industrial estates have provided a range of new industrial lots with a range of small to medium sized modern office/warehouse/workshop facilities that have all been recently constructed and present to a high standard.

*approx

- Air conditioned offices

- Electric roller door 4m wide x 5m high
- Rear roller door to small yard 3.6m wide x 5m high
- Engineering mezzanine floor in warehouse 3m wide x 14m long (3 metre height clearance under mezzanine floor)
- 4 car bays
